dct_title_s: State of New Jersey Board of Commerce and Navigation riparian survey of Toms River
dct_description_sm: This survey of Toms River consists of six maps in a black/white copy. The segmented maps show coastal and riparian information including river depth and sounding measurement as well as local property development and street grids. The quality of these maps is poor and they are blurry/double exposed.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
Survey map is incomplete. It is missing one sheet.
